FBIS4-28625 "dreas113_d_94018" FBIS-EAS-94-113 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 South Korea Briefs ROK Counterpart by Phone Briefs ROK Counterpart by Phone SK1306075294 Seoul YONHAP in English 0744 GMT 13 Jun 94 SK1306075294 Seoul YONHAP English BFN [Text] Seoul, June 13 (YONHAP) -- Foreign Minister Han Sung-chu talked with his Japanese counterpart Koji Kakizawa, who is visiting China, over the telephone Monday and agreed to push for gradual sanctions against North Korea. In their telephone conversation lasting 10 minutes from 12:40 p. m. (KST), Kakizawa briefed Han on his meeting with Chinese Foreign Minister Qian Qichen to discuss the North Korean nuclear problem, Ministry spokesman Chang Ki-ho said.
